%% Diagram: Connection lifecycle — connect, heartbeat, reconnect with backoff
%% Type: stateDiagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Connecting: open()
    Connecting --> Open: handshake ok
    Connecting --> Backoff: handshake error
    Open --> HeartbeatSent: ping interval elapsed
    HeartbeatSent --> Open: pong received
    HeartbeatSent --> Closing: pong timeout
    Open --> Closing: close frame / network drop
    Closing --> Backoff: not auth or rate-limit error
    Closing --> [*]: 401 / explicit shutdown
    Backoff --> Connecting: delay = min(base * mult^n + jitter, cap)
    Backoff --> [*]: max attempts reached
    note right of Backoff
        Exponential backoff with jitter.
        Reset attempts on first successful Open.
        Honor Retry-After on 429.
    end note
    note left of Open
        On reconnect: replay pending mutations
        and request missed messages by lastSeq
        or Last-Event-ID.
    end note
